devdoc.details: Implementation of the team token vesting

addTeamMember(address,uint256).details: Add a new team member to withdrawal tokens.

params.tokenAmount: The token amount desired by the team member

isOwner().return: true if `msg.sender` is the owner of the contract.

nextWithdrawalTime(address).details: Get the next withdrawal day of the user.

remainingTokenAmount(address).details: Get the remaining token for some member.

renounceOwnership().details: Allows the current owner to relinquish control of the contract.

terminateTokenVesting().details: Clean everything and terminate this token vesting

totalAlocatedWibxVestingTokens().details: Returns all tokens allocated to users.

totalWibxVestingSupply().details: Get the token supply in this contract to be delivered to team members.

transferOwnership(address).details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.

params.newOwner: The address to transfer ownership to.

withdrawal(address).details: Withdrawal team tokens to the selected wallet

devdoc.title: WiBX Token Vesting

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.
